      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Psychedelic Integration: Making Meaning Last</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Integration is the process of making meaning from a psychedelic experience and translating what arose into a changed way of living and relating. The experience loosens habitual patterns and expands what is possible to perceive — but loosening is not the same as changing. Integration is the sustained work of embodying what was encountered. It gives the psychedelic experience lasting significance, and without it, even the most profound journeys tend to fade without lasting effect.</p>
